node.text: A big congratulations to @jthammavongsa and Eric on their recent engagement!!! This video literally gave me chills and all of us at Forever Diamonds NY are ecstatic that you chose us to be a part of this magical moment. Wear it in good health and send us all the pictures!!!

node.text:
Our team couldn’t be more thrilled to congratulate @britneyspears and @samasghari on the beginning of their Forever 💍💕

The thought and detail Sam put into this ring made the design process so special for Roman and our team. In honor of the Lioness herself, we are naming this gorgeous setting The Britney.

Sam and Britney, we wish you a lifetime of happiness together and are honored to welcome you to the Forever Diamonds Family ❤️

Find more details about Britney’s ring at the link in our bio 📱 

#britneyspears #foreverdiamondsny #samasghari #DENGRA01775
